          EnumMap<LessonType,Integer> credits

          String description
          Optional description of the course.
        • gradeBook
          HashMap<Student,Mark> gradeBook

          GradeReport gradeReport
          Grade report associated with the course.
        • lessonID
          int lessonID
          Counter for generating unique lesson IDs.
        • prerequesites
          HashSet<Course> prerequesites
          Set of prerequisite courses required for enrollment in this course.

          Semester semester
          Semester in which the course is offered.
